ha that `=` sign looks like a `-` sign in your screenshot.
One thing you can try to do is avoid placing a `dnd_module` as a direct child of a `dnd_section` as that is interpretting the width attribute of the module as part of the dnd grid.
```{% dnd_section full_width=true %}
  {% dnd_column %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module path='@HubSpot/divider', width=50 %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
  {% end_dnd_column %}
{% end_dnd_section %}```
